Class Vector2

  • java.lang.Object
    • Utils.Vector2

  • public class Vector2
extends java.lang.Object

    Vector2

    A two-dimensional vector that stores two floating point values to represent a position in 2D space and is capable of basic transformations.

    Since:
    28-02-2019
    Version:
    1.0
